This is a checklist of planned features with notes on how to implement them

ANIMATION FEATURES

    Complete gui for animation controls including highlighting current frame

    Add ability to create and remove animations

    Add ability to add selected sprite definitions to current animation

    Add relevent buttons to for animation editing including
        - increasing number of frames in the animation
        - reducing the number of frames in the animation
        - consided adding ability to scroll frames, de facto removing max frame cap
    
    Decide whether an animation should use one palette or each sprites palette (1 is practical)
